label.value: EC 1.* (oxidoreductase) inhibitor

definition.value: An enzyme inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase (EC 1.*.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.1.* (oxidoreductase acting on donor CH-OH group) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on the CH-OH group of donors (EC 1.1.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.2.* (oxidoreductase acting on donor aldehyde/oxo group) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on the aldehyde or oxo group of donors (EC 1.2.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.3.* (oxidoreductase acting on donor CH-CH group) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on the CH-CH group of donors (EC 1.3.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.4.* (oxidoreductase acting on donor CH-NH2 group) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on the CH-NH2 group of donors (EC 1.4.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.5.* (oxidoreductase acting on donor CH-NH group) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on the CH-NH group of donors (EC 1.5.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.6.* (oxidoreductase acting on NADH or NADPH) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on  NADH or NADPH (EC 1.6.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.8.* (oxidoreductase acting on sulfur group of donors) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase of class EC 1.8.*.* (acting on a sulfur group of donors).

label.value: EC 1.9.* (oxidoreductase acting on donor heme group) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on a heme group of donors (EC 1.9.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.10.* (oxidoreductase acting on diphenols and related substances as donors) inhibitor

label.value: EC 1.11.* (oxidoreductase acting on peroxide as donors) inhibitor

label.value: EC 1.13.* [oxidoreductase acting on single donors with incorporation of molecular oxygen (oxygenases)] inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on single donors with incorporation of molecular oxygen (oxygenases), EC 1.13.*.*.

label.value: EC 1.14.* (oxidoreductase acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on hydrogen as donors (EC 1.14.*.*).

label.value: EC 1.17.* (oxidoreductase acting on CH or CH2) inhibitor

definition.value: An oxidoreductase inhibitor which interferes with the action of an oxidoreductase acting on CH or CH2 (EC 1.17.*.*).

label.value: EC 3.* (hydrolase) inhibitor

definition.value: Any enzyme inhibitor that interferes with the action of a hydrolase (EC 3.*.*.*).

label.value: EC 3.1.* (ester hydrolase) inhibitor

definition.value: A hydrolase inhibitor that interferes with the action of any ester hydrolase (EC 3.1.*.*).

label.value: EC 3.5.* (hydrolases acting on non-peptide C-N bonds) inhibitor

definition.value: Any hydrolase inhibitor that interferes with the action of a hydrolase acting on C-N bonds, other than peptide bonds (EC 3.5.*.*).

label.value: EC 3.1.1.* (carboxylic ester hydrolase) inhibitor

definition.value: An EC 3.1.* (ester hydrolase) inhibitor that interferes with the action of a carboxylic ester hydrolase (EC 3.1.1.*).

label.value: EC 3.1.3.* (phosphoric monoester hydrolase) inhibitor

definition.value: An EC 3.1.* (ester hydrolase) inhibitor that interferes with the action of any phosphoric monoester hydrolase (EC 3.1.3.*).

label.value: EC 3.4.21.26 (prolyl oligopeptidase) inhibitor

definition.value: Any EC 3.4.21.* (serine endopeptidase) inhibitor that interferes with the action of prolyl oligopeptidase (EC 3.4.21.26).

label.value: EC 3.4.15.* (peptidyl-dipeptidase) inhibitor

definition.value: Any EC 3.4.* (hydrolases acting on peptide bond) inhibitor that interferes with the activity of a peptidyl dipeptidase (EC 3.4.15.*).

definition.value: An EC 3.1.* (ester hydrolase) inhibitor that interferes with the action of any endoribonuclease producing 5'-phosphomonoesters (EC 3.1.26.*).

label.value: EC 2.4.2.* (pentosyltransferase) inhibitor

label.value: EC 2.5.1.18 (glutathione transferase) inhibitor

label.value: EC 6.3.1.* (acid-ammonia/amine ligase) inhibitor

label.value: EC 5.99.1.* (miscellaneous isomerase) inhibitor

label.value: EC 1.13.11.* (oxidoreductase acting on single donors and incorporating 2 O atoms) inhibitor

label.value: EC 1.14.13.* (oxidoreductase acting on paired donors, incorporating 1 atom of oxygen, with NADH or NADPH as one donor) inhibitor

label.value: vancomycin(1+)

definition.value: An organic cation that is the conjugate acid of vancomycin, obtained by deprotonation of the carboxy group and protonation of the two amino functions; major species at pH 7.3.
